      "<a href="http://oauth.net/grant_type/assertion/saml/2.0/bearer">http://oauth.net/grant_type/assertion/saml/2.0/bearer</a>" to
      "<a href="http://oauth.net/grant_type/saml/2.0/bearer">http://oauth.net/grant_type/saml/2.0/bearer</a>" - dropping the word
      assertion from the path.  Recent versions of <a href="./draft-ietf-oauth-v2">draft-ietf-oauth-v2</a>
