      this URI is more reflective of that.  It also more closely aligns
      with the grant type URI in <a href="./draft-jones-oauth-jwt-bearer-00">draft-jones-oauth-jwt-bearer-00</a> which
      is "<a href="http://oauth.net/grant_type/jwt/1.0/bearer">http://oauth.net/grant_type/jwt/1.0/bearer</a>".

   o  Added "case sensitive" to scope definition to align with
      <a href="./draft-ietf-oauth-v2-15">draft-ietf-oauth-v2-15</a>/16.

